OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779793371
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman dies
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a woman was found
OL,8,Funresponsive.
OL,10,FThe woman, believed to be in her 40s,
OL,11,Fwas discovered after officers were
OL,12,Fcalled to Tweedale Street in Rochdale
OL,13,Fabout 4pm on Monday, 26 May. She died
OL,14,Fat the scene.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed a
OL,17,Fman in his 30s was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of murder and was in custody.
