PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779793371
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman dies
OL,6,FEnquiries to formally identify the
OL,7,Fwoman and establish the circumstances
OL,8,Fsurrounding her death are ongoing, the
OL,9,Fforce said.
OL,11,FTemporary Detective Chief
OL,12,FSuperintendent Jamie Daniels said: "We
OL,13,Fappreciate this incident is likely to
OL,14,Fcause some distress amongst the public
OL,15,Fand local community.
OL,17,F"I would like to reassure you that we
OL,18,Fbelieve this to be an isolated
OL,19,Fincident, which does not pose any
OL,20,Ffurther risk to the wider public.
OL,26,@tD@dOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
