OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779793371
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman dies
OL,6,F"Our priority at this time is
OL,7,Fconducting formal identification of
OL,8,Fthe victim and informing her family as
OL,9,Fsoon as we can. Specialist officers
OL,10,Fwill be available to support them
OL,11,Fduring this difficult time.
OL,13,F"We understand the severity of events
OL,14,Fsuch as this, and whilst we are in
OL,15,Fvery early stages, our officers will
OL,16,Fwork tirelessly to establish the full
OL,17,Fdetails of this tragic death."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@^O]
